  "content_html": "<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-1a0c8643-f2ac-4326-8871-035b7c77878d\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-fa5ae9e1-d693-42c2-bce3-a744295fc511\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-3fd6c261-483b-46ae-bd10-db63c8603536\" style=\"color:#555555;\">안녕하세요.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-165bddbe-4289-4aed-925b-8a7ca33d4f4a\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-cbb8fb2b-b07f-445d-b4f5-61b343037edc\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>단상자,</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-ea40f965-2daa-46fd-bdc0-d54d7584fad0\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-b213c275-851c-4921-8396-3f119989429c\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>골판지 합지,</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-c5139024-09dd-4ce7-8d7f-5e0b89524562\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-bca5e0aa-a1f9-452f-ae1b-acd53beee6d9\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>싸바리 박스 생산은</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-9b7d2f29-973b-4a52-8b9f-e9f17f028773\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-8174a932-b6a7-402e-9545-7e73638293e0\" style=\"color:#ff0010;\"><b>(주)파파스컴퍼니</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-ba12b1e6-f886-434e-929d-311e7e5682eb\" style=\"color:#555555;\">입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-c9a1099b-751d-43af-90e2-da9789224f44\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-center\" style=\"max-width:595px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223986881851/000.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-dff02985-e4f6-4c80-864d-f30918e1f253\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-6ea0cb2d-55d4-4aa9-9bc7-ea9ea3e13043\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-026734ee-65a0-406d-87b9-17c61dc1e23a\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#fdd5f5;\">단상자 중에 가장 사랑받는 접착방식이 삼면 접착입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-1c40987f-8b54-4268-8683-03e0a3aab9cf\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-c1b6a872-ce3e-492c-9c8d-ef21a4fbbde8\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-dd4507e2-20ed-44d7-85e5-229cd6e78d81\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-1dd8a7e9-b055-46a0-8dce-13efa0536388\" style=\"color:#555555;\">삼면접착은 하단 두 곳과 옆면을 붙여 끼워 맞추는 형태로 제작됩니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-c7a64918-1c67-485b-b3cd-f117a933a43d\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:771px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223986881851/001.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-95a5148f-e0b9-4eb3-9696-4b0d7ff88dc6\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-0e3c3653-c532-4e5d-9d39-9837c41a1d32\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-94055b1e-2437-4334-a6fa-2cb96036ea7f\" style=\"color:#555555;\">이 편리한 삼면접착은 다음과 같은 장단점이 존재합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-7733a58c-b2ee-4b8b-a0ca-74768d2cd1b1\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-84c76275-533d-4060-afdd-82459cac4b81\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-c3aafb85-3f29-4dbe-859a-936c5c9ae27f\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-959d10fa-f049-49d5-a02e-f0419e377aa4\" style=\"color:#555555;\">첫째, 단상자 형태 중에 3면을 접착하기 때문에 </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-ccf4c7e7-242a-4616-9636-f98a061301a2\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>단가가 약간 비싸질 수 있습니다. </b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-6643c974-a622-4e6e-a07e-edf7925d219e\" style=\"color:#555555;\">맞뚜껑이나 십자조립형은 옆면만 부착하는 반면에 삼면접착은 하단에 두 번 접착하는 방식이므로 단가가 조금 비싸질 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-fb551667-4c72-4ed0-b76a-72e77ef6f720\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-0c3ae529-df56-41e0-a07b-3e072e04afb5\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-4ebe955a-7b23-46ff-8093-fab94016a0c6\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-a4f3aa2c-8ef5-4ecd-8a96-88fe6f1b7224\" style=\"color:#555555;\">두 번째, </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-400dbcd0-2ff8-44c7-a5a1-3731b481cda6\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>전개도 도면이 틀리면 잘 안 끼워지는 사고가 발생</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-c5da90ec-4a27-4f47-999e-6e86d49fe6b6\" style=\"color:#555555;\">할 수 있습니다. 그러므로 반드시 전문 목형집과 거래를 하시고 제작하시기를 추천드립니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-bfe1ce5b-779b-452f-a9e3-5fef93d9b4f4\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-5886001c-ce82-49bb-8ec7-b89d0e41dccc\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-9f85627a-928e-4cfc-9e1a-6e75cefce3f4\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-174bcdfa-0883-4c76-ab90-cb9fe9a14437\" style=\"color:#555555;\">세 번째는 강점으로 </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-653ea11c-e68b-43bc-a5cc-4d773dc027e7\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>조립시간이 편하고 빠릅니다</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-56244152-5183-4119-a670-6eb94c409425\" style=\"color:#555555;\">. 빠르게 제품을 넣고 조금 더 단단하게 하단을 고정시킬 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-97c8c0a9-818d-46e8-9e80-c6977887bfb3\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-b191ea0e-7d6b-46f1-a49e-780764a412f3\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-75375154-667e-43ac-921a-2df6c7fdc62e\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-a9692869-b23f-4955-ba14-d7e17b4d37d2\" style=\"color:#555555;\">그러면 이제는 주의점 3가지를 알아보겠습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\" id=\"SE-a474e3bb-b37d-4262-8893-805e60b609c4\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-9d9c3b90-eda6-4597-90ef-37cfafddcf66\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-d308a2c1-a267-41a2-9fcd-e6ab56730653\" style=\"\">삼면접착시 주의점 : 뚜껑의 스톱바 논쟁</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-51f1726e-9338-4d7d-bded-a910b3faa62d\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-5b99d696-38b8-43fa-861c-4670aec44d45\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-6c63d30b-0707-4432-acd1-04187a1feef1\" style=\"color:#555555;\">뚜껑을 스톱바 말고 양눈섭의 눈오시로만 작업하세요.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-d98c2a40-685e-4b00-8561-9aa76044d901\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:283px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223986881851/002.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-6a99236b-0f37-484d-b1c7-b21b0ab8201f\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-8c98817f-b64d-4c24-8dc2-535f0a196ad4\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-739741b2-50c7-48ba-9a17-358106067c2f\" style=\"color:#555555;\">위 뚜껑은 요즘 트렌드에 맞는 양쪽 눈오시로 작업하세요. 물론 이 부분이 재작업 사유가 될 수는 없습니다. 하지만 요즘은 뚜껑을 잘 열기 위해 과거처럼 스톱바로 칼집을 내지는 않습니다. 특히 디지털 소량의 디지털 커팅의 경우 아래 스톱바 작업 시에는 작은 문제가 발생될 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-76aedfce-b740-4f0e-8cce-79fc1c81139e\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-134cf179-7d32-4daf-adbf-fb8addb9e4b3\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-e3ac8596-d7f5-4ea5-acb0-681764afb56d\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-040e70ea-c301-450b-ac20-9d14f8487bfd\" style=\"color:#555555;\">하지만 이 부분은 100% 잘못된 것이라고 말씀드리는 것은 아닙니다. 여전히 스톱바로도 작업을 많이 하십니다. 특히 양쪽을 여는 맞뚜껑의 경우는 하단은 스톱바 윗면은 오시로 작업을 가장 많이 하십니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-df72b1d9-abd3-4b26-8443-cc318b5947c8\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-70aa07bc-4570-4424-a8df-c7c64b9dc33d\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\" id=\"SE-31c6404b-199f-4b00-b4ab-baae56a28541\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-7cb7de54-11c8-4aa0-90a5-08f639e039b6\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-b3761fdb-4a4f-458d-9af4-3d5ab50f79a8\" style=\"\">삼면접착시 주의점 : 접히는 부분의 곡선화</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-6f580e2c-cc2d-4644-b804-672fabc1332f\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:595px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223986881851/003.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-219986eb-7ef0-45ba-b634-3a4f5a14bed5\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-22868a0e-c998-4299-bc44-683930c17a74\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-ee98c9fd-d678-48b3-89f8-532edecab8ad\" style=\"color:#555555;\">오시는 넣는 칼선 부분은 반드시 곡선으로 자연스럽게 만들어야 합니다. 이렇게 작업이 이루어져야만 접을 때 도는 따낼 때 사고가 나지 않습니다. 특히 디지털 커팅을 하는 소량의 경우는 더 그렇습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-83b3066a-2840-4e00-80c4-98f6d3b9cccd\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-97d515de-51bb-49fb-a275-21cc27cd12bb\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-ea04f7a2-05a2-4708-b360-aca35eacffd8\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:479px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223986881851/004.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-6e0999ac-8164-4d03-83c1-dab85d5efb65\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-7e4f28ff-41d5-4860-b123-946abf483c07\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-4161e491-ca42-4d1a-a2f9-f66accab98a6\" style=\"color:#555555;\">만드신 칼선이 이렇게 생겼다면 반드시 문제가 발생됩니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-3f3c3aeb-389b-4e5e-8418-afce46cd7b8e\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:478px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223986881851/005.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-2842e857-1eb2-447d-9775-e5256b445329\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-2a74a2d0-a1b6-448b-84b2-fb59ec4ac6e8\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-cbc79a81-458c-42db-8a26-375060b5df5d\" style=\"color:#555555;\">이렇게 만들어져야 문제가 없다는 뜻입니다. 이 부분은 중요합니다. 전문적인 칼선 제작 업체에 의뢰하여 목형을 만드세요.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-2171f601-ffc6-4e35-9651-6b9573b1c5f4\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-982cdbda-43dc-4a0e-a4ec-1a0347172151\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-0f530a81-8e3f-4a97-b6b4-12867da59ffc\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-75457148-850e-4292-99b9-e4d6b031346e\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\" id=\"SE-08dd2183-4dbc-46c8-adaa-d626eba215ba\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-49a812f3-adb8-4d58-ae37-6fa7cc02e9d7\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-a2f99038-c661-4854-a64a-8c94aa733107\" style=\"\">삼면접착시 주의점 : 하단 접착면 인쇄 색상</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-cef107c5-7cbb-4680-bcdc-d6d540f93483\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223986881851/006.jpg\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-6d889432-6efc-4a82-a037-aca29ba0f402\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-437a6b37-ef51-48cc-8d9c-07baf1189763\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-b1743020-18de-42ce-833f-9e742c872f08\" style=\"color:#555555;\">과거에는 하단 접착면에 인쇄가 들어가면 접착이 잘 안된다고 하여 인쇄면을 잘랐습니다. 하지만 요즘은 접착 기술의 발달로 모든 면에 인쇄를 해도 무방합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-a1b31e31-81c9-47d3-b30c-066ae3c49fc7\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:595px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223986881851/007.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-c75a1770-aa19-41e5-9ec5-1055f5086c37\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-5be694c8-9678-4573-9f3f-9ef610ea00ff\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-a5b31eea-0284-42ce-91de-b2e168386d24\" style=\"color:#555555;\">과거에는 인쇄면을 자르거나 접착면에 인쇄나 코팅이 침범하지 않게 디자인했었습니다. 하지만 요즘은 인쇄를 끝까지 다 해서 접착을 합니다. 이렇게 하면 더 깔끔하고 경계면이 보이지 않습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-65e8d58c-0611-4191-81f4-d004840e7476\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:595px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223986881851/008.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-044a9963-a3b2-4452-b323-49d125d95975\">\n<div cl